name: dream garden
description:
"Dream garden" I have found you! Walking between green leafs, juicy red apples and white little birds. Tears to my eyes, tears of grace. Thank you garden, thank you for your loving embrace, joy and tenderness. I will remember you always, even in the deepest of my nightmares. 🙏

Hand drawn GIF | Classical Guitar 
Visual and music by Moodan.
Paris, 2022.
